{"tid":1330952,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[香城online] 破陣!!!","createTime":"2019-07-18T18:28:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T17:25:16.000Z","uid":62776,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"788c402d570512e249b2da71da3643421420fe3d","tid":1330952,"uid":62776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T18:28:25.000Z","msg":"大家要知道<br />\n香城online入面狗狗要攻<br />\n一定會有陣式<br />\n佢地一定會冇後顧之憂先夠膽盡情向前攻<br />\n所以我地一定要係佢地後方做成混亂!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n長盾陣<br />\n<br />\n基本上一定係一字排開<br />\n前面架盾<br />\n務求盡擋示威者既攻擊<br />\n但同時黎講<br />\n後面就有破綻<br />\n要掃走呢班垃圾狗狗<br />\n只需要<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一支地拖同一條有返30m左右粗麻繩!!!</span></span><br />\n只要將條麻繩<br />\n綁係地拖中間位<br />\n要死結實既<br />\n再將支地拖掉去狗狗後面<br />\n示威者有10個8個一齊撤退跑<br />\n一齊拉住條繩<br />\n咁地拖棍就會掃低d狗狗<br />\n因為佢地個陣要一字排開<br />\n加上係緊貼<br />\n所以一支地拖棍起碼掃低3，4件<br />\n一掃低左<br />\n佢地個陣就要停<br />\n會將個攻勢暫停左<br />\n而且拉完返黎又可以再掟過<br />\n希望呢個方法可以幫到大家爆機打關<br />\n<br />\n祝各位武運昌隆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d26c929604ab8a356f29f706dad907b1452691ea","tid":1330952,"uid":62776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T18:29:18.000Z","msg":"自推攻略"},{"pid":"8a08905b652f80f25682a801d46229b703df745d","tid":1330952,"uid":62776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T18:30:52.000Z","msg":"大家一齊俾d意見啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4cb0caef128eb6f8de2b0b69fbb07358d085e08","tid":1330952,"uid":62776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T18:35:40.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"f062e7c05b749488c507a3af36ef91ac2a36f64a","tid":1330952,"uid":62776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T01:01:33.000Z","msg":"再自推下先"},{"pid":"afced31cb6812cedfa3585c413c79790b9974fc9","tid":1330952,"uid":131884,"like":0,